Bsdk Bete!!!
Bhai sahab tujhe toh ab Tusaand bhi nhi bula skta bahut shi transformation kiya hai yaar tu mujhse agar koi poochhega ki dedication kise kehte hain main tera naam bolunga...yaar amazing hai tu...kitna chill rhta hai bhai.kabhi kabhi lgta hai ki itna chill kaise ho skta hai tu ki sala agle immediate step ki parwah nhi krta..wing me tere ko naveen ke oopar chad ke pole dance krna ho, solar panels pe chdna ho, farsh pe slide krna ho.. bsdk drr nhi lgta tereko...hamesha chaapta hai saala acads me...saath me class jana..voh class ke baad ccd canteen se chai lekar stage pe baithna..bahut sukoon tha unn shamon me...Photoshoot ke liye itna excited...ek aur baat jo achhi lgti hai teri voh hai ki kahin bhi apna ek dominance bnane ki koshish krna: chahe bolleyball, cricket, photoshoot, treat ho..sala har jagah aage rhna hai bsdvale ko...bahut amazing hai bhai tu...baaki ka sb kuchh likhna toh thoda mushkil hai..aur haan teri last vali advice hmesha yaad rkhunga thanks for that......milte hain bhai jaldi hi
